■join() 메서드

예시1
items = ('apple', 'banana', 'kiwi')
print('->'.join(items))
#  apple->banana->kiwi

예시2
딕셔너리도 된다 (.key())
HowMany = {'dog': 2, 'lion': 5, 'pig': 1}
print(" ".join(HowMany.keys()))
#  dog lion pig

예시3
lines = ['First line', 'Second line', 'Third line']
result = '\n'.join(lines)
print(result)
#  First line
   Second line
   Third line




■print() 내부에서

예시1
items = ('apple', 'banana', 'kiwi')
print(items, sep = " & ")
#  apple & banana & kiwi
